<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu na dawnna bang ahim,
 Tuni'n a hun hukdam nuom?
 &quot;Ei hun zuonin&quot; ti'n A hun chiel,
 Bang dinga vaigei nalai ding?

[V2]
 Isu nei sam hi tih ka hei,
 Nang apat vakmang ta puong ka;
 Tho in ka Hukdampa zuon ka,
 Lawp dingin Ama'n ei na ngak.

[V3]
 2. Na vaigeih banga phachuom ding?
 Na niel leh na tha mangthai ding;
 Isu lo hukdam thei umlo,
 Kross thihna'n Ama'n A din tai.

[V4]
 3. Isu nang tan dinga thi kha,
 Mun hun bawlsak di'n a chieh;
 Lopina ah A hun na ngak,
 Amah zuonin, vakmang takin.</lyrics>
<title>WHAT IS YOUR ANSWER TO JESUS?</title>
<hymn_number>181</hymn_number>
</song>